						</v8:item>
						<v8:item>
							<v8:lang>en</v8:lang>
							<v8:content>&lt;color #000000&gt;To grant access &lt;/&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;color #000000&gt;independent of working groups.
These settings widen other permissions and do not cancel them.</v8:content>
